3. Capacity addition or product launch 

3.1. Capacity addition:  
a) existing capacity;  
b) existing capacity utilization;  
c) proposed capacity addition;   
d) period within which the proposed capacity is to be added;  
e) investment required;   
f) mode of financing;   
